import { MainContainer, Titulo } from '../../styles'
import { Campo } from '../../styles'

const Formulario = () => (
  <MainContainer>
    <Titulo>Nouvelle tâche</Titulo>
    <form>
      <input type="text" placeholder="Titre" />
      <textarea placeholder="Description de la tâche" />
      <input name="prioridade" type="radio" id="urgente" />{' '}
      <label htmlFor="urgente">Urgent</label>
      <input name="prioridade" type="radio" id="iimportante" />{' '}
      <label htmlFor="importante">Important</label>
      <input name="prioridade" type="radio" id="mormal" />{' '}
      <label htmlFor="normal">Normal</label>
      <button type="submit">Registre</button>
    </form>
  </MainContainer>
)

export default Formulario
